default Operation ATRIUM is an education and enforcement campaign led by the City of London Police.
default CRISP – Cycle Route Implementation and Stakeholder Plan. This is part of TfL’s develop
defaultment procedures for implementation of cycling schemes.
default Operation FOIST was a large scale, multi-agency operation conducted by the MPS to tackle all types of crime associated with motor vehicles
default. Large numbers of illegally operated motor vehicles were rem
defaultoved from the roads of east London’s streets. This continues, but at a smaller scale as operation CUBO.
